OL,3,CNew galleon arrives ready for revamp
OL,4,Cof Diana memorial playground
OL,6,FThe centrepiece of a #3 million revamp
OL,7,Fof the Diana, Princess of Wales
OL,8,FMemorial Playground ` a 17 metre-long
OL,9,Fgalleon ` has been lifted into place
OL,10,Fin its new London home.
OL,12,FThe wooden ship, built from mountain
OL,13,Flarch in the foothills of the Bavarian
OL,14,FAlps, made its maiden voyage, ready
OL,15,Ffor its installation in Kensington
OL,16,FGardens.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
