OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772197440
OL,3,CNew galleon arrives ready for revamp
OL,4,Cof Diana memorial playground
OL,6,FThe upgraded play area will feature
OL,7,Fthe galleon, including a tunnel slide,
OL,8,Ftwo crow's nests and a ramped entrance
OL,9,Fto the main deck for disabled access,
OL,10,Fas well as a new treehouse, a
OL,11,Fredesigned water play area and a new
OL,12,Funder-threes zone.
OL,14,FBuilt in tribute to the late princess,
OL,15,Fwho was killed in a car crash in 1997,
OL,16,Fthe free playground, next to Diana's
OL,17,Fformer home, Kensington Palace, first
OL,18,Fopened in 2000.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
