PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772197440
OL,3,CNew galleon arrives ready for revamp
OL,4,Cof Diana memorial playground
OL,6,FThe Royal Parks charity said the #3
OL,7,Fmillion was being spent after the
OL,8,Fprevious equipment "reached the end of
OL,9,Fits life".
OL,11,FThe attraction, which has an average
OL,12,Fof one million visitors per year,
OL,13,Fmaking it the UK's most visited
OL,14,Fplayground, has been closed for the
OL,15,Frefurbishment works since last autumn,
OL,16,Fbut is due to reopen in the summer.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
