CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772197440
OL,3,CNew galleon arrives ready for revamp
OL,4,Cof Diana memorial playground
OL,6,FAndy Williams, park manager for
OL,7,FKensington Gardens, said: "We are
OL,8,Fdelighted to have the new galleon `
OL,9,Fthe centrepiece of the Diana Princess
OL,10,Fof Wales Memorial Playground ` here in
OL,11,FKensington Gardens.
OL,13,F"Children can be the captain of their
OL,14,Fown ship and let their imaginations
OL,15,Fsoar when the playground reopens in
OL,16,Fsummer 2026."
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOUxD@MO]
