PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1772197440
OL,3,CNew galleon arrives ready for revamp
OL,4,Cof Diana memorial playground
OL,6,FThe galleon was constructed in the
OL,7,Fvillage of Frasdorf, Germany, by
OL,8,FTimberplay and its partners Richter
OL,9,FSpielgerate, the same designers who
OL,10,Fproduced the original Peter Pan-themed
OL,11,Fgalleon when the playground first
OL,12,Fopened.
OL,14,FRoyal Parks said the harsh alpine
OL,15,Fconditions result in extremely slow
OL,16,Fgrowth, making the timber stronger and
OL,17,Fnaturally rot-resistant, negating the
OL,18,Fneed for chemically treated wood.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
